---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ScrollIndicator from '../../components/ScrollIndicator.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Simulation Room (Test Cell) | EES"
  description="Controlled testing under real-world conditions using our purpose-built simulation room, aligned to ASHRAE-55 and ISO 7730 standards."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Simulation Room</h1>
      <p>Controlled testing under real-world conditions.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>Real Conditions, Measured Results</h2>
      <p>
        Our simulation room replicates the thermal behaviour of a real occupied space — not a sealed box in a lab. With a north-facing 7.5m² glass wall, insulated walls to Australian standard, and full environmental monitoring, we test how products actually perform in conditions people live and work in.
      </p>

      <h2>Testing Standards</h2>
      <p>All evaluations are conducted in accordance with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>ASHRAE Standard 55</strong> — Thermal Environmental Conditions for Human Occupancy</li>
        <li><strong>ISO 7730</strong> — Ergonomics of the thermal environment</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How Testing Works</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Baseline measurement</strong> — we characterise the room's thermal behaviour without any conditioning system active</li>
        <li><strong>System installation</strong> — the product under test is installed as it would be in a real building</li>
        <li><strong>Controlled scenarios</strong> — we run heating, cooling, and mixed-mode tests across a range of outdoor conditions</li>
        <li><strong>Data collection</strong> — all sensors log continuously, capturing comfort metrics, energy consumption, and system response times</li>
        <li><strong>Analysis &amp; reporting</strong> — results are compiled into a performance report with recommendations</li>
      </ol>

      <p>
        Want to test your product in our facility? <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <ScrollIndicator />
</BaseLayout>
